Adding remote client folder

1. Added the main.cpp file that single cpp source file that reads the image file from a serial connection, processes the image to count the number of faces and sends this information to the non-remote freewave device from which it is uploaded to cloud via AWS.
2. Added a README.txt file that contains the build command for main.cpp file.
